{"ocr_results":[{"text":"(2)","box":[[756,86],[802,86],[802,113],[756,113]]},{"text":"In l982 they started a new readjustment in the jiguan in Beijing.","box":[[265,151],[1323,155],[1322,185],[264,181]]},{"text":"Before 1978 hires, everyone was 8","box":[[184,184],[714,189],[713,217],[184,212]]},{"text":"given a raise of one grade unless they","box":[[702,187],[1324,189],[1324,218],[702,216]]},{"text":"made a mistake.","box":[[183,220],[432,221],[432,245],[183,244]]},{"text":"One example, a case he heard of through a friend he worked","box":[[459,220],[1409,220],[1409,250],[459,250]]},{"text":"with.A married worker who had an affair with an unmarried girl and got","box":[[182,250],[1357,255],[1357,282],[182,277]]},{"text":"caught was given a reprimand (jiguo) and didn't get a raise。A","box":[[183,283],[1202,286],[1202,315],[183,312]]},{"text":"Another","box":[[1189,290],[1307,290],[1307,310],[1189,310]]},{"text":"worker had been locked up for fighting and didn't get one。(","box":[[182,316],[1169,320],[1169,347],[182,343]]},{"text":"Others were","box":[[1155,320],[1342,322],[1341,346],[1155,344]]},{"text":"denied them for stealing f","box":[[186,347],[602,351],[602,378],[186,374]]},{"text":"factory materials and selling them.","box":[[589,351],[1201,353],[1201,380],[589,378]]},{"text":"Middle aged","box":[[1188,354],[1373,354],[1373,378],[1188,378]]},{"text":"intellectuals were 8","box":[[185,382],[501,386],[501,410],[185,406]]},{"text":"given a raise of two grades。","box":[[493,387],[988,387],[988,411],[493,411]]},{"text":"College graduates before","box":[[978,384],[1374,383],[1374,414],[978,415]]},{"text":"1960, l966 and below a certain pay grade for these levels of seniority","box":[[183,414],[1325,417],[1325,447],[183,444]]},{"text":"were given 2 grades。","box":[[184,452],[549,452],[549,476],[184,476]]},{"text":"It was all decided by a central document。","box":[[539,450],[1249,452],[1249,479],[539,477]]},{"text":"The technical","box":[[1240,452],[1454,452],[1454,476],[1240,476]]},{"text":"school graduates were eligible for this only if they had reached the rank","box":[[183,480],[1375,483],[1375,512],[183,509]]},{"text":"of engineer or lecturer.","box":[[184,514],[574,516],[574,543],[184,541]]},{"text":"A problemin1977and1979hadbeenthat the attendance restriction was","box":[[264,547],[1422,548],[1422,575],[263,574]]},{"text":"6mos。}","box":[[183,579],[322,584],[321,608],[182,603]]},{"text":"You could be absent for 5 months and 29 days, and still get a raise.","box":[[307,580],[1421,582],[1421,612],[307,610]]},{"text":"That was not a good way to do it。","box":[[183,613],[754,616],[753,643],[183,640]]},{"text":"People taking","box":[[753,616],[971,618],[971,642],[752,640]]},{"text":"long","box":[[964,620],[1049,620],[1049,641],[964,641]]},{"text":"leaves and still were","box":[[1063,617],[1406,616],[1406,640],[1063,641]]},{"text":"getting","box":[[184,650],[304,648],[305,671],[185,674]]},{"text":"raises。","box":[[293,651],[431,651],[431,672],[293,672]]},{"text":"Sothey solved it this way:","box":[[457,647],[926,650],[926,676],[457,672]]},{"text":"they","box":[[937,651],[1002,651],[1002,672],[937,672]]},{"text":"figured the entire previous","box":[[1016,651],[1452,649],[1452,672],[1016,675]]},{"text":"3 years","box":[[185,679],[301,683],[300,708],[184,704]]},{"text":"6together--nomorethanone yearleavein 3y","box":[[291,681],[1025,681],[1025,708],[291,708]]},{"text":"years。","box":[[1013,685],[1134,685],[1134,706],[1013,706]]},{"text":"There was a big","box":[[1143,681],[1391,684],[1391,707],[1143,705]]},{"text":"problem","box":[[184,716],[304,712],[305,736],[185,739]]},{"text":"nof","box":[[293,715],[351,715],[351,737],[293,737]]},{"text":"f people using connections with doctors to get sick leave certifi-","box":[[337,712],[1407,711],[1407,741],[337,742]]},{"text":"cates。","box":[[186,749],[302,747],[303,768],[186,770]]},{"text":"It","box":[[312,747],[349,747],[349,767],[312,767]]},{"text":":is still a widespread problem caused by free medicine and sick","box":[[339,746],[1375,746],[1375,773],[339,773]]},{"text":"pay. This was basically the way","box":[[182,776],[715,776],[715,809],[182,809]]},{"text":"theydid it in thefactory beginning in","box":[[720,778],[1358,779],[1358,806],[720,805]]},{"text":"the fall of l983，with their new readjustments。","box":[[185,809],[954,813],[954,839],[185,835]]},{"text":"People didn't have an","box":[[980,811],[1326,810],[1326,838],[980,839]]},{"text":"opinion about this was of doing it。","box":[[185,843],[790,845],[789,872],[185,869]]},{"text":"You didn't have any contradictions","box":[[784,845],[1340,845],[1340,872],[784,872]]},{"text":"arising because all was fixed by the center。‘","box":[[186,875],[937,876],[937,904],[186,903]]},{"text":"They had already finished","box":[[933,878],[1340,878],[1340,902],[933,902]]},{"text":"their wage readjustment before he left。1","box":[[185,907],[858,909],[858,939],[185,937]]},{"text":"By March in Beijing it","box":[[847,910],[1216,910],[1216,937],[847,937]]},{"text":"wasalready","box":[[1203,912],[1403,912],[1403,936],[1203,936]]},{"text":"done。","box":[[187,944],[292,944],[292,965],[187,965]]},{"text":"They also ignored problems 'left over by history'--this was to be","box":[[292,939],[1359,940],[1359,971],[292,970]]},{"text":"solved later.","box":[[182,972],[397,976],[397,1003],[181,999]]},{"text":"Bonuses","box":[[182,1039],[299,1042],[298,1067],[181,1064]]},{"text":"They restored bonuses in l978。 There were initially no fixed regulations。","box":[[265,1073],[1468,1073],[1468,1100],[265,1100]]},{"text":"They gave about 6-7 yuan a month.  In 1979 Deng came back and things changed.","box":[[183,1104],[1436,1104],[1436,1134],[183,1134]]},{"text":"They","box":[[184,1139],[257,1142],[256,1166],[183,1163]]},{"text":"I said that the yearly bonus can't be more than the factory's average","box":[[242,1136],[1358,1139],[1358,1169],[242,1166]]},{"text":"wage for 1.5 months。","box":[[181,1173],[538,1170],[538,1197],[181,1200]]},{"text":"In 1983 they adopted a new spirit:factory performance","box":[[556,1171],[1454,1173],[1454,1200],[556,1198]]},{"text":"was the","box":[[183,1207],[303,1205],[304,1229],[183,1231]]},{"text":"epoint of emphasis。","box":[[291,1206],[643,1207],[643,1231],[291,1230]]},{"text":"The second criteria was that the amount can't be","box":[[637,1204],[1422,1203],[1422,1230],[637,1231]]},{"text":"over 5% of the profit remitted to the state。","box":[[183,1236],[941,1238],[941,1265],[183,1262]]},{"text":"This was beguntheendof 1978.","box":[[933,1239],[1439,1239],[1439,1262],[933,1262]]},{"text":"Factories had little power, and had to get permission for how much to pay out.","box":[[180,1267],[1456,1267],[1456,1300],[180,1300]]},{"text":"After they got the amount approved, the leading cadres met and decided how","box":[[182,1301],[1394,1301],[1394,1334],[182,1334]]},{"text":"to distribute the funds。","box":[[186,1336],[592,1336],[592,1360],[186,1360]]},{"text":"They assessed your work, problems, etc., and divided","box":[[607,1335],[1458,1335],[1458,1365],[607,1365]]},{"text":"people into 3 gradesaccording","box":[[184,1370],[681,1369],[681,1396],[184,1397]]},{"text":"to the final decisions made","box":[[687,1369],[1136,1368],[1136,1395],[687,1396]]},{"text":"eby","box":[[1124,1371],[1182,1371],[1182,1393],[1124,1393]]},{"text":"leading cadres.","box":[[1192,1371],[1437,1371],[1437,1395],[1192,1395]]},{"text":"Even top leaders got bonuses。","box":[[184,1404],[689,1404],[689,1428],[184,1428]]},{"text":"They set different amounts for shops, offices.","box":[[688,1400],[1437,1401],[1437,1431],[688,1430]]},{"text":"Inourdepartment","box":[[183,1436],[464,1439],[464,1462],[183,1458]]},{"text":"t grade1 was 10 yuan，2 9 yuan，and 38 yuan。","box":[[451,1435],[1224,1435],[1224,1461],[451,1461]]},{"text":"They had","box":[[1224,1433],[1361,1436],[1360,1464],[1224,1461]]},{"text":"problems because in the offices the work is all about the same, everyone","box":[[182,1467],[1358,1467],[1358,1497],[182,1497]]},{"text":"works about the same pace.。","box":[[182,1500],[644,1502],[644,1529],[182,1527]]},{"text":"Hard to assess work performance。","box":[[638,1501],[1192,1503],[1192,1527],[638,1525]]},{"text":"They would","box":[[1192,1501],[1360,1501],[1360,1528],[1192,1528]]},{"text":"deduct from your bonus based on the leave you took, no matter what kind of","box":[[184,1533],[1394,1533],[1394,1563],[184,1563]]},{"text":"leave it was。","box":[[183,1567],[400,1569],[400,1594],[183,1592]]},{"text":"They did not have group assessments in the office.","box":[[423,1566],[1244,1565],[1244,1595],[423,1596]]},{"text":"Year end bonus.","box":[[265,1601],[549,1603],[549,1627],[264,1625]]},{"text":"Themoney","box":[[537,1601],[695,1604],[694,1627],[537,1623]]},{"text":"left over at the end of the year was given","box":[[699,1598],[1392,1601],[1392,1628],[699,1625]]},{"text":"out as a year end bonus equally","box":[[182,1635],[697,1632],[697,1659],[182,1662]]},{"text":"toall。1","box":[[685,1636],[859,1636],[859,1656],[685,1656]]},{"text":"Egalitarianism.","box":[[847,1634],[1098,1632],[1098,1656],[848,1659]]},{"text":"Later on they","box":[[1128,1630],[1343,1635],[1342,1662],[1128,1657]]},{"text":"criticized egalitarianism, than they had 3 grades, about 32,30, 28 yuan.","box":[[182,1662],[1358,1664],[1358,1694],[182,1692]]},{"text":"That's what they reported to the above levels, but in reality all got the","box":[[182,1698],[1377,1698],[1377,1728],[182,1728]]},{"text":"same amount.","box":[[181,1736],[377,1734],[377,1758],[181,1760]]},{"text":"The progressive elements would be assessed at the end of the year in","box":[[261,1765],[1377,1762],[1377,1792],[262,1795]]},{"text":"small groups。","box":[[182,1798],[426,1801],[426,1828],[182,1824]]},{"text":"According to your work and technical level.","box":[[424,1799],[1135,1797],[1135,1824],[424,1826]]},{"text":"This small","box":[[1157,1800],[1324,1800],[1324,1821],[1157,1821]]},{"text":"number would be given a prize of l0 yuan in addition every year.","box":[[180,1831],[1230,1831],[1230,1860],[180,1860]]},{"text":"The system overall is basically no different than the supplementary","box":[[261,1861],[1360,1863],[1360,1894],[260,1892]]},{"text":"wages of the past。","box":[[182,1901],[513,1901],[513,1925],[182,1925]]},{"text":"Just about everybody got something。I think only the","box":[[504,1898],[1375,1897],[1375,1924],[504,1925]]}],"dimensions":{"height":2133,"width":1565}}